		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Super Dodge Ball is MMC1, as is Vs. Dr. Mario. Unfortunately, the MDS-VS1 board only supports 64 KiB PRG/CHR, and Super Dodge Ball is 128/128, so there would be some rework there...<br /><br />Super Dodge Ball also stops reading from $4017 if you select a one-player game.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


